Titolo: Gateway (video game)

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: Frederik Pohl's Gateway is a 1992 interactive fiction video game released by Legend Entertainment, and written by Glen Dahlgren and Mike Verdu. It is based on Frederik Pohl's Heechee universe. It was followed by a sequel Gateway II: Homeworld, in 1993.
In 1996 Legend Entertainment made the game available for free download from its website.